  "text": "RT-PCR analysis. All tumor cells, endothelial cells, and primary epithelial cells were analyzed by PCR for expression of VEGFA189, VEGFA165, VEGFA121, VEGFB186, VEGFB167 and VEGFD, and the receptors VEGFR1, VEGFR2, NRP1, NRP2 and EGFR. Human ß-actin was used as positive control. For this, RNA was isolated and reverse transcribed as described previously [CITATION_1] . Sequences are given in Table I . PCR products were separated with agarose gel electrophoresis. Table I . RT-PCR primer pairs. Table II . Real-time RT PCR primer sets.",
